COMMAND: protection from evil <spell points>
COST: Varies
DURATION: Varies
LEVEL: ANY

Will reduce damage done to you by 1/3 from evil creatures. 
The amount of damage the shield can absorb is based on the Paladins
level and their piety and how many spell points spent. The minumum amount 
of spell points must be 50 the maximum is 250.

Each time the shield is hit it will give you a 'Strength:' msg.
This indicates how much damage the shield has absorbed.
A strenght of 100% means it has absorbed no damage, 60% means it's
absorbed 40% of its maximum amount, and so on.....

